1.
define method, take two integers as parameters, perform addition,
returns result

START

SET method, with two ints as parameters
READ first parameter
READ second parameter
return first + second parameter

END

2.
define method, takes array of strings as parameter, strings concatenated

START

SET method, takes array of strings as parameter
  WHILE array has more strings
    READ each string
    concatenate all the strings together
    return the result

END

3.
define method, take array of ints as parameter,
return every second element as a new array

START

SET method, takes array of ints as parameter
  WHILE there are more elements
    READ element
      IF element index is dividable by 2
        put element in a new array

  return new array

END
